div.p:
yathā khalv ayo 'bhyāsamantareṇāyaskāntamupasarpati
evamāhārābhyāsamantareṇa bālaḥ stanyamabhilaṣati
// 23 //

'svaguṇān nopalabhante indriyāṇītyetanna
bhavati-- upalabhyate hi svaguṇaḥ śabdaḥ śrotreṇeti
// 72 //

yathānādiḥ prāgutpatterabhāva utpannena bhāvena nivartyate
evaṃ svābhāvikī kleśasaṃtatiranityeti
// 66 //

apara āha-- yathānādiraṇuśyāmatā atha
cāgnisaṃyogādanityā tathā kleśasaṃtatirapīti
// 67 //

kṣutpipāsābhyāṃ śītoṣṇābhyāṃ vyādhibhiścānicchatopi
buddhayaḥ pravartante tasmādaikāgryā nupapattiriti
// 40 //

vigṛhyeti vijigīṣayā na tattvabubhutsayeti, tadedat
vidyāpālanārthaṃ na lābhapūjākhyātyarthamiti
// 51 //
